    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is very solid; the engine runs smoothly without any unusual noises, and the transmission shifts precisely through all gears. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear on the driver's seat, and all electronics are fully functional. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper consistent with normal use. It\u2019s a dependable car that\u2019s ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
