    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic vehicle! It's in good condition and has been clearly well-maintained, offering a smooth and dependable ride that you're going to love. This is a wonderful opportunity to own a reliable, high-quality car that's ready for its next adventure!",
